               class="crossfade-img" 
               alt="Close-up of ebony handle for custom camp knife"
               loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/vitrine/Détails-table-olivier.webp" 
               class="crossfade-img" 
               alt="Olive wood handle finish on fine dining knife"
               loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/vitrine/Détails-grand-bonap-satiné.webp" 
